### =========================================================
### User-Auth End-to-End Scenario Pack
### =========================================================
### 목적
### - 실제 업무 흐름 순서대로 API를 실행하기 위한 시나리오 모음
### - IntelliJ HTTP Client 기준 (@name + client.global.set 사용)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 계정 샘플 (환경에 맞게 변경)
@platformEmail = platform.admin@attestry.local
@platformPassword = PlatformAdm1n!2026

@ownerEmail = scenario.owner@attestry.io
@ownerPassword = Password123!
@ownerPhone = 010-1111-2222

@operatorEmail = scenario.operator@attestry.io
@operatorPassword = Password123!
@operatorPhone = 010-3333-4444

@templateOwnerCore = TEMPLATE_TENANT_OWNER_CORE
@templateWork = TEMPLATE_BRAND_WORK

### 수동 입력 fallback 값
@tenantId = REPLACE_TENANT_ID
@membershipId = REPLACE_MEMBERSHIP_ID
@invitationId = REPLACE_INVITATION_ID
@applicationId = REPLACE_APPLICATION_ID


### =========================================================
### [Scenario A] 사용자 준비: 회원가입 + 로그인
### =========================================================

### A-1) Owner signup (이미 존재하면 409 가능)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{ownerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{ownerPassword}}",
  "phone": "{{ownerPhone}}"
}

### A-2) Operator signup (이미 존재하면 409 가능)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{operatorEmail}}",
  "password": "{{operatorPassword}}",
  "phone": "{{operatorPhone}}"
}

### A-3) Platform login
# @name platformLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{platformEmail}}",
  "password": "{{platformPassword}}",
  "tenantId": null
}

> {%
  client.global.set("platformAccessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### A-4) Owner login (온보딩 승인 후 tenant 포함 재로그인 권장)
# @name ownerLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{ownerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{ownerPassword}}",
  "tenantId": null
}

> {%
  client.global.set("ownerAccessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}


### =========================================================
### [Scenario B] 온보딩 + 승인 + 기본 운영자 초대/권한 부여
### =========================================================

### B-1) 증빙 presign
# @name presignEvidence
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/evidences/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "evidenceBundleId": null,
  "fileName": "biz-proof-1.pdf",
  "contentType": "application/pdf"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("evidenceBundleId", response.body.evidenceBundleId);
  client.global.set("evidenceFileId", response.body.evidenceFileId);
  client.global.set("uploadUrl", response.body.uploadUrl);
%}

### B-2) presigned URL 업로드
PUT {{uploadUrl}}
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./files/biz-proof-1.pdf

### B-3) 증빙 complete
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/evidences/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "evidenceBundleId": "{{evidenceBundleId}}",
  "evidenceFileId": "{{evidenceFileId}}",
  "sizeBytes": 102400
}

### B-4) 브랜드 신청
# @name createBrandApplication
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/applications
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "BRAND",
  "orgName": "SCENARIO_BRAND",
  "country": "KR",
  "bizRegNo": "110-11-56382",
  "evidenceBundleId": "{{evidenceBundleId}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("applicationId", response.body.applicationId);
%}

### B-5) 플랫폼 관리자: 신청 승인
# @name approveBrandApplication
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/onboarding/applications/{{applicationId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{platformAccessToken}}

> {%
  client.global.set("tenantId", response.body.tenantId);
  client.global.set("ownerMembershipId", response.body.membershipId);
%}

### B-6) Owner tenant 컨텍스트로 재로그인
# @name ownerTenantLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{ownerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{ownerPassword}}",
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("ownerTenantAccessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### B-7) 플랫폼 관리자: tenant role-template 바인딩 (operator)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/role-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{platformAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "roleCode": "TENANT_OPERATOR",
  "templateCode": "{{templateWork}}"
}

### B-8) Owner: 운영자 초대
# @name inviteOperator
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{operatorEmail}}",
  "role": "STAFF"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("invitationId", response.body.invitationId);
%}

### B-9) Operator login
# @name operatorLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{operatorEmail}}",
  "password": "{{operatorPassword}}",
  "tenantId": null
}

> {%
  client.global.set("operatorAccessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### B-10) Operator: 초대 수락
# @name acceptInvitation
POST {{baseUrl}}/invitations/{{invitationId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorAccessToken}}

> {%
  client.global.set("operatorMembershipId", response.body.membershipId);
%}

### B-11) Owner: Operator role 부여
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{operatorMembershipId}}/roles/TENANT_OPERATOR
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}

### B-12) Owner: 테넌트 사용 가능 템플릿 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/permission-templates/available
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}

### B-13) Owner: Operator에게 작업 템플릿 적용
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{operatorMembershipId}}/permission-templates/{{templateWork}}/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "scenario operator work grant"
}

### B-14) Owner: Operator 역할/권한 상태 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{operatorMembershipId}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}


### =========================================================
### [Scenario C] 정책 검증(실패 케이스)
### =========================================================

### C-1) Operator가 TENANT_OWNER 부여 시도 (정책상 403 기대)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{operatorMembershipId}}/roles/TENANT_OWNER
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorAccessToken}}

### C-2) Operator가 template 적용 시도 (정책상 403 기대)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{operatorMembershipId}}/permission-templates/{{templateOwnerCore}}/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "should be denied"
}

### C-3) Owner가 자기 자신에게 TENANT_OWNER 재부여 (self escalation 가드 확인)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{ownerMembershipId}}/roles/TENANT_OWNER
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}


### =========================================================
### [Scenario D] Authz evaluate 확인
### =========================================================

### D-1) LIVE_RECHECK 평가
POST {{baseUrl}}/authz/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "action": "TENANT_ROLE_ASSIGN",
  "resourceRef": "membership:{{operatorMembershipId}}",
  "decisionMode": "LIVE_RECHECK"
}

### D-2) tenant mismatch 평가 (deny 기대)
POST {{baseUrl}}/authz/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerTenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "wrong-tenant-id",
  "action": "TENANT_ROLE_ASSIGN",
  "resourceRef": "membership:{{operatorMembershipId}}",
  "decisionMode": "TOKEN_SNAPSHOT"
}
